name: DIY Tattoo Themed Watermelon Flower, Clover Horseshoe, or Clover Wishbone Cross Stitch Pattern
description:
Sweet as Watermelon!

and it uses 8 DMC colors. The stitch can be bigger or smaller if you choose to use 14 count or 18 count. I can change the colors if you would like, just message me.

You will receive a .pdf file of the pattern within an hour after purchasing it. I will also be available for any questions you might have.
